data.description: Rarely available Arbor Lakes Duplex with the square footage & layout that truly makes it feel like a single family home. Featuring 4 spacious bedrooms including a master suite with double vanity, oversized soaker tub, tiled shower, & his & hers closets, 2.5 bathrooms, eat-in kitchen with white cabinets, granite countertops, oversized island with seating for four, stainless steel appliances, pantry & backsplash, full finished basement provides more entertaining space with a large rec room/additional family room, the backyard is fenced & has large patio & was recently professionally landscaped. Other features/upgrades include: luxury vinyl plank floors installed on main level (2022), widened driveway, open railings along the staircase, sump pump with battery backup, professionally installed window treatments, professionally painted throughout. The subdivision has NO SSA & a low annual HOA of $300 per year. This home is part of accredited Minooka School District. Close to shopping, restaurants, parks, and bike paths. Easy access to highway for easy commute. Current contract/buyer has a home to sell contingency - showings still welcome! Schedule your showing today!
